Class AuthenticationResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.microsoft.identity.client.AuthenticationResult

  • public final class AuthenticationResult
extends java.lang.Object
    MSAL success authentication result. When auth succeed, token will be wrapped into the AuthenticationResult and sent back through the AuthenticationCallback.
